# 🎵 JavaScript Music Player

A simple and responsive music player built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It supports basic playback controls like play/pause, next/previous track, and displays track information.

## 🚀 Features
- Play/pause functionality
- Next and previous track navigation
- Dynamic track title display
- Responsive design

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## 📁 File Structure
project-folder/ │ ├── index.html # Main HTML file 
├── style.css # Styling for the player 
├── script.js # JavaScript logic 
└── music/ # Folder containing .mp3 files




## 📦 Setup Instructions
1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Add your `.mp3` files to the `music/` folder.
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.
4. Enjoy your music!

